## 4. Notion-like Shared Workspace (March 3, 2026)
- **Database Architecture:** [WorkspaceDocument](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/lib/workspaceApi.ts#3-24) schema upgraded with `icon`, `order`, and `collaborators` fields to support customizable pages and sharing.
- **Backend API:** Extended `workspace` domain to accept JSON-based component rendering data, icon settings, and specific user access scopes.
- **Frontend Refactor ([tasks/page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/app/%28app%29/tasks/page.tsx)):**
  - Completely replaced the cramped 3-pane layout with a spacious **2-pane Notion-style editor**.
