  - **Dynamic Editor Canvas:** Documents now support block-based content via a custom Widget Engine.
  - **Right-Click Context Menu:** Added intuitive `shadcn/ui` Context Menu anywhere in the document canvas to insert widgets.
  - **Widgets Included:**
    - [NoteWidget](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/components/workspace/widgets/note-widget.tsx#13-43): Auto-resizing rich text areas.
    - [TaskWidget](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/components/workspace/widgets/task-widget.tsx#18-94): Inline checklist/Kanban task tracker.
    - [TableWidget](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/components/workspace/widgets/table-widget.tsx#15-130): Dynamic data grid with row/column insertion bindings.
- **Performance:** Implemented debounced auto-saving (1000ms) to ensure seamless typing and widget manipulation under load.

